== Months of Kōgo ==
In a [[Common Era]] year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (that is, when the [[十干]] are {{ill|Xin|ja|辛}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙}}), the month of {{ill|January|ja|1月}} becomes the [[Month (Calendar)|month]] of Kōgo. However, here the term “month” may refer either to the month of the [[Lunisolar]] or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Risshun|ja|立春}} until the day before {{ill|Keichitsu|ja|啓蟄}}) as applicable.

