'''Yang Metal Tiger also known as 甲午 (kanoetora, koukinnotora, kouin)''' is one of the [[Sexagenary cycle]].

It is the 27th combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Jichū|ja|己丑}} and the following combination is {{ill|Xinyou|ja|辛卯}}. In the system of [[陰陽五行思想]] (Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory), the [[十干]] element {{ill|Jia|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)}} represents yang [[木]] (Wood) and the [[Earthly Branches]] element {{ill|Tiger|ja|寅|1=Tiger (zodiac)|lt=Tiger (寅)}} represents yang [[火]] (Fire), and they interact by [[五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|Mutual Overcoming]] (Metal overcomes Wood).

