== Months of Kōgo ==
In a [[Common Era]] year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (that is, when the [[十干]] are {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|January|ja|1月|12=draft|12=draft}} becomes the [[Month (Calendar)|month]] of Kōgo. However, here the term “month” may refer either to the month of the [[Lunisolar]] or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Risshun|ja|立春|12=draft|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Keichitsu|ja|啓蟄|12=draft|12=draft}}) as applicable.

== Days of Kōgo ==
The [[Day Selection|selection]] for a Kōgo day is as follows.
=== Day Selection ===
A Kōgo day is the 7th day of {{ill|Toppōkure|ja|十方暮|12=draft|12=draft}}.
