=== Events ===
* In the 4th Year of {{ill|Empress Jitō|ja|持統天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Empress Jitō|qq=}} (690 AD) – the "Kōgo Nenseki" (庚寅年籍) was completed and implemented.

== Months of Kōgo ==
In a [[Common Era]] year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (that is, when the [[十干]] are {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|January|ja|1月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/January|qq=}} becomes the [[Month (Calendar)|month]] of Kōgo. However, here the term “month” may refer either to the month of the [[Lunisolar]] or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Risshun|ja|立春|1=Lichun|lt=Risshun|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Risshun|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Keichitsu|ja|啓蟄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichitsu|qq=}}) as applicable.

== Days of Kōgo ==
The [[Day Selection|selection]] for a Kōgo day is as follows.
=== Day Selection ===
A Kōgo day is the 7th day of {{ill|Toppōkure|ja|十方暮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toppōkure|qq=}}.
