It is the 27th combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Jichū|ja|1=Yin Earth Ox|2=ja|己丑|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jichū|qq=}} and the following combination is {{ill|Xinyou|ja|1=Yin Metal Rabbit|2=ja|辛卯|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xinyou|qq=}}. In the system of [[Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory]], the [[Heavenly Stem]] {{ill|Kinoe (甲)|ja|甲|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)}} represents yang [[Wood (wuxing)|Wood]] and the [[Earthly Branches]] element {{ill|Tiger|ja|寅|1=Tiger (zodiac)|lt=Tiger (寅)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tiger|13=User:Immanuelle/Tiger (zodiac)|qq=}} represents yang [[Fire (wuxing)|Fire]], and they interact by Mutual Overcoming (Metal overcomes Wood).
[[ja:庚寅]]
