{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Metal Tiger|kanji=庚寅|romaji=kanoe tora|onyomi=kōin|p=gēngyín|w=keng-yin|mi=kɤŋ⁵³ ȵin²¹|y=geng1 jan4|j=geng1 jan4|ci=kɪŋ jɐn|mc=kæŋ ŋin|oc-bs=kˤraŋ ŋin|qq=}}
{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}}

'''Yang Metal Tiger also known as 庚寅 (kanoetora, koukinnotora, kouin)''' is one of the [[Sexagenary cycle]].

It is the 27th combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Jichū|ja|1=Yin Earth Ox|2=ja|己丑|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jichū|qq=}} and the following combination is {{ill|Xinyou|ja|1=Yin Metal Rabbit|2=ja|辛卯|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xinyou|qq=}}. In the system of [[Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory]], the [[Heavenly Stem]] {{ill|Kinoe (甲)|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|lt=Kinoe (甲)|2=ja|3=甲|4=zh|5=甲|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)}} represents yang [[Wood (wuxing)|Wood]] and the [[Earthly Branches]] element {{ill|Tiger|ja|寅|1=Tiger (Zodiac)|lt=Tiger (寅)|2=ja|3=寅|1=Tiger (zodiac)|lt=Tiger (寅)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tiger|13=User:Immanuelle/Tiger (zodiac)|qq=}} represents yang [[Fire (wuxing)|Fire]], and they interact by Mutual Overcoming (Metal overcomes Wood).
[[ja:庚寅]]
== Years of Kōgo ==
A year in the [[Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 30 when divided by 60 is a year of Kōgo.
