'''Yang Metal Tiger also known as 庚寅 (kanoetora, koukinnotora, kouin)''' is one of the [[Sexagenary cycle]].
It is the 27th combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Jichū|ja|1=Yin Earth Ox|2=ja|己丑|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jichū|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jichū|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Ox|qq=}} and the following combination is {{ill|Xinyou|ja|1=Yin Metal Rabbit|2=ja|辛卯|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xinyou|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xinyou|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Metal Rabbit|qq=}}. In the system of [[Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory]], the [[Heavenly Stem]] {{ill|Kinoe (甲)|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|lt=Kinoe (甲)|2=ja|3=甲|4=zh|5=甲|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=}} represents yang [[Wood (wuxing)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|Wood]] and the [[Earthly Branches]] element {{ill|Tiger|ja|寅|1=Tiger (Zodiac)|lt=Tiger (寅)|2=ja|3=寅|1=Tiger (zodiac)|lt=Tiger (寅)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tiger|13=User:Immanuelle/Tiger (zodiac)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tiger|13=User:Immanuelle/Tiger (Zodiac)|qq=}} represents yang [[Fire (wuxing)|ja|Fire (火)|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (火)|2=uk|3=Вогонь (У-сін)|4=bcl|5=Kalayo (wuxing)|6=pt|7=Fogo (astrologia)|8=vi|9=Hỏa (Ngũ hành)|10=ar|11=النار (وو شينغ)|lt=Fire (火)|Fire]], and they interact by Mutual Overcoming (Metal overcomes Wood). [[ja:庚寅]] == Years of Kōgo == A year in the [[Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 30 when divided by 60 is a year of Kōgo. {| class="wikitable" |+ '''Years of Kōgo''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 34|34 AD]] * [[:en:AD 94|94 AD]] * [[:en:154|154 AD]] * [[:en:214|214 AD]] * [[:en:274|274 AD]] * [[:en:334|334 AD]] * [[:en:394|394 AD]] * [[:en:454|454 AD]] * [[:en:514|514 AD]] * [[:en:574|574 AD]] * [[:en:634|634 AD]] * [[:en:694|694 AD]] * [[:en:754|754 AD]] * [[:en:814|814 AD]] * [[:en:874|874 AD]] * [[:en:934|934 AD]] * [[:en:994|994 AD]] | * [[:en:1054|1054 AD]] * [[:en:1114|1114 AD]] * [[:en:1174|1174 AD]] * [[:en:1234|1234 AD]] * [[:en:1294|1294 AD]] * [[:en:1354|1354 AD]] * [[:en:1414|1414 AD]] * [[:en:1474|1474 AD]] * [[:en:1534|1534 AD]] * [[:en:1594|1594 AD]] * [[:en:1654|1654 AD]] * [[:en:1714|1714 AD]] * [[:en:1774|1774 AD]] * [[:en:1834|1834 AD]] * [[:en:1894|1894 AD]] * [[:en:1954|1954 AD]] | * [[:en:2014|2014 AD]] * {{ill|2074 AD|ja|2074年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2074|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2074 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2134 AD|ja|2134年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2134|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2134 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2194 AD|ja|2194年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2194|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2194 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2254 AD|ja|2254年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2254|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2254 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2314 AD|ja|2314年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2314|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2314 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2374 AD|ja|2374年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2374|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2374 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2434 AD|ja|2434年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2434|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2434 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2494 AD|ja|2494年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2494|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2494 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2554 AD|ja|2554年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2554|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|