=== Events === * In the 4th Year of [[:en:Empress Jitō|Empress Jitō]] (690 AD) – the "Kōgo Nenseki" (庚寅年籍) was completed and implemented.
==Months of Yang Metal Tiger== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (that is, when the [[十干]] are {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|lt=Kanoto (辛)|2=ja|3=辛|4=zh|5=辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|lt=Hinoe (丙)|2=ja|3=丙|4=zh|5=丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:January|January]] becomes the [[Month (Calendar)|month]] of Kōgo. However, here the term “month” may refer either to the month of the [[Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|Lunisolar]] or to a seasonal month (from [[:en:Lichun|Risshun]] until the day before [[:en:Jingzhe|Keichitsu]]) as applicable.
==Days of Yang Metal Tiger== The [[Day Selection|selection]] for a Kōgo day is as follows. === Day Selection === A Kōgo day is the 7th day of {{ill|Toppōkure|ja|十方暮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toppōkure|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toppōkure|qq=}}. == See Also == * {{prefix|qq=}} * {{intitle|qq=}}
